{"word":"G3947 - παροξύνω - paroxýnō - par-ox-oo'-no - Easily provoke","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παροξύνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>paroxýnō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>par-ox-oo'-no"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Easily provoke"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வைராக்கியமடை, சினமடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to stimulate, spur on, urge, to make sharp, to sharpen"},{"paragraph":"2. to irritate, provoke, rouse to anger"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G3691 - ὀξύς - oxýs - oz-oos'/3691\">G3691</a>; to <i>sharpen alongside</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>exasperate:</i> - easily provoke, stir."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3947 - παροξύνω - paroxýnō - par-ox-oo'-no/3947\">G3947</a>, <a href=\"#/G3948 - παροξυσμός - paroxysmós - par-ox-oos-mos'/3948\">G3948</a>"}]}